Quickstrike:










Quickstrike watched as Sinester walked away from he and Sinesis. His leg 
hurt like crazy, with the brace on his leg Tarantsulus' clone made for him 
broken. He slowly sat up.

"What in tarnation was that fer?" he asked Sinesis.

He grunted from the pain in his leg.
